                     <td align="right"><a class="menu" href="JavaScript:OpenWindow20()"><img src="http://www.ahsaniamission.org.bd/wp-content/themes/wisdom/images/presenter.gif" border="0"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.ahsaniamission.org.bd/knowledge/Community_Score_Card.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.ahsaniamission.org.bd/wp-content/themes/wisdom/images/topics.gif" border="0"></a></td>
